## 11. Docker Compose Setup

```yaml
version: "3.9"
services:
  backend:
    build: ./backend
    ports:
      - "${APP_PORT}:8000"
    volumes:
      - ./data:/app/data        # SQLite DB persists here
    env_file: .env
    restart: unless-stopped

  frontend:
    build: ./frontend
    ports:
      - "3000:3000"
    depends_on:
      - backend
    restart: unless-stopped
```

- SQLite file lives in `./data/` which should be mapped to a Synology shared folder for easy backup
- No external database container needed

