## 13. Error Handling

|Scenario                  |Behaviour                                                                                                    |
|--------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|Gemini API rate limit hit |Status в†’ `failed`, error message shown in UI with retry button                                               |
|Invalid ticker            |TradingAgents returns error в†’ caught, stored, shown in UI                                                    |
|DS218+ loses power mid-run|Status stays `running` on restart вЂ” UI should show a вЂњstaleвЂќ warning for runs stuck in `running` for >30 mins|
|Gemini API key missing    |App refuses to start, logs clear error message                                                               |

